* {{transliteration|ja|[[:en:Ame no Wakahiko sōshi (otogi-zōshi)|Ame no Wakahiko sōshi]]}}
* {{transliteration|ja|[[Komachi Sōshi]]}}
* {{transliteration|ja|[[Koshikibu (one-volume otogi-zōshi)|Koshikibu]]}} (I)
* {{transliteration|ja|[[Koshikibu (two-volume otogi-zōshi)|Koshikibu]]}} (II)
